request: GET, /api/v1/contas-receber/18170476
assert: expected **200** to equal **200**

assert: expected **{ Object (id, origem, ...) }** to contain keys **id**, **origem**, **origemId**, **notaFiscal**, **quantidadeParcelas**, **recorrencia**, **tipoIntervalo**, **observacao**, **createdAt**, **valorTotalClinica**, **itens**, **parcelas**, **tipoPagador**, **voucher**, **status**, **tipoReceita**, **fornecedor**, **paciente**, and **profissional**
assert: expected **[ Array(1) ]** to be an array

assert: expected **{ Object (id, descricao, ...) }** to contain keys **id**, **descricao**, **quantidade**, **valorUnitario**, **valorTotal**, **valorTotalClinica**, **executado**, **classificacaoFinanceira**, and **executante**
assert: expected **{ Object (id, classificacaoFinanceira) }** to contain keys **id**, and **classificacaoFinanceira**
assert: expected **{ Object (id, nomeFantasia) }** to contain keys **id**, and **nomeFantasia**
assert: expected **[ Array(1) ]** to be an array

assert: expected **{ Object (id, dataVencimento, ...) }** to contain keys **id**, **dataVencimento**, **numeroParcela**, **valor**, **observacao**, **status**, **liquidacoes**, **valorPago**, and **valorPagar**
assert: expected **{ id: 1, status: Não quitadas }** to contain keys **id**, and **status**
assert: expected **[]** to be an array
assert: expected **{ id: 1, liquidante: PACIENTE }** to contain keys **id**, and **liquidante**
assert: expected **{ id: 1, status: Não quitadas }** to contain keys **id**, and **status**
assert: expected **{ Object (id, tipoRecebimento) }** to contain keys **id**, and **tipoRecebimento**
